snippet.title: Moon River Release Video
snippet.description:
My first game project, Moon River is out!
A short game with an emphasis on music and atmosphere. Perhaps some secrets too...
It's available for free right now!

itch.io:
⬇️ https://badalias.itch.io/moonriver

RPG Maker Network:
⬇️ https://rpgmaker.net/games/13124/

....
You can also download the soundtrack for free on Bandcamp, too.
🎵 https://badalias.bandcamp.com/album/moon-river-original-soundtrack
